taken an "eHarmony" approach to mentor matching, and combined it with actionable intelligence and innovative mobile technology. We''re the only solution available with our technology to help mentoring programs not only better manage day-to-day operations, but also better engage mentors and mentees.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">In addition, Dream Extreme is:</h3>\r\n<ul style="text-align: center;">\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Scalable</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Customizable</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">White-labeled</li>\r\n	<li style="text-align: left;">Affordable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">We''re not just ''technology people.'' We''re mentors, too. We know how important your work is, and we''ve built Dream Extreme to help you stretch your dollars and get it done.</p>', 'How Mentoring works', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mentoring', '', '', '2015-11-22 00:28:09', '2015-11-22 00:28:09', '', 0, 'http://dreamplanner.campuslifeohs.com/?page_id=25', 0, 'page', '', 0),
